  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  women with PCOS in accordance with Rotterdam criteria

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnancy

          -  diabetes mellitus (or impaired glucose tolerance as determined by a standard 75 gr
             oral glucose tolerance test)

          -  past history of cardiovascular diseases

          -  past history of gastro-intestinal diseases

          -  significant liver or renal dysfunction (hypothalamic, pituitary, thiroidal or
             adrenal);

          -  neoplasms.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
